---

## WHO READS WHAT

### Claude Web reads (via Janis downloading to Project Knowledge — NOT repo)
- chat_rules.md           — every Claude Web session, auto via project knowledge
- workflow_skill.md       — every Claude Web session, auto via project knowledge

### Claude Web NEVER reads directly from repo.
### cc NEVER reads chat_rules.md or workflow_skill.md.

---

### cc reads — EVERY session start (in this exact order)
1. cc_rules.md            — process and coding rules, non-negotiable
2. knowledge.map          — this file
3. cc_chat_log.md         — Claude Web flags and last session status
4. /prompts/[task].md     — today's specific task file (filename given by Janis in chat)

### cc reads — ONLY when task requires
- .claude/rules-codes.md     — any SCAD task
- rules-dimensions.md        — any SCAD task (in repo root)
- .claude/rules-materials.md — any SCAD task
- .claude/rules-vm.md        — VM tasks only
- rules-pr.md                — PR tasks only (create when needed)
- .claude/SKILL_problem_solving_kt.md — R-111 trigger
- .claude/SKILL_joint_construction.md — any T-junction or mismatched cross-section transition fix/build
- .claude/SKILL_product_design_skeleton.md — READ FIRST (before this whole list) for any NEW product line that is not VM-01 or PR-01. Grandfather clause: VM-01/PR-01 are explicitly exempt, never retrofitted.
- latest .scad file          — active model only (filename in cc_chat_log.md)

